16:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"2026-yilga ko'ra O'zbekistonda jismoniy shaxslarning daromad solig'i (JShShS) stavkasi 12% ni tashkil etadi. Bu barcha turdagi daromadlarga — ish haqi, dividendlar, tadbirkorlik faoliyatidan olingan daromadlar, royalti va boshqa to'lovlarga qo'llaniladigan yagona tekis stavkadir. Norezidentlar ham O'zbekistondagi manbalardan olingan daromadlardan 12% stavkada JShShS to'laydilar. IT Park rezidentlari uchun imtiyozli 7,5% stavka amal qiladi, bu O'zbekistonni Markaziy Osiyoda IT-mutaxassislar uchun eng jozibador yurisdiktsiyalardan biriga aylantiradi. Soliq ish beruvchi (soliq agenti) tomonidan har oy ish haqi to'lanayotganda ushlab qolinadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"JShShSdan tashqari, O'zbekistonda ish haqidan majburiy ajratmalar ushlab qolinadi: 12% miqdorida ijtimoiy soliq (byudjet tashkilotlari uchun — 25%), shuningdek individual jamg'arma pensiya hisobvarag'iga ("}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ish-haqi","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"IJPH"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":") to'lov — hisoblangan ish haqining 0,1%. Shunday qilib, ish haqi fondiga umumiy soliq yuki sezilarli ulushni tashkil etadi. Ish beruvchi ijtimoiy soliqni o'z hisobidan to'laydi, JShShS va IJPH esa xodimning ish haqidan ushlab qolinadi. 2025-yil avgustidan boshlab bazaviy hisoblash kattaligi ("}],["$","$La","3",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","4",{"children":") 412 000 so'm ga teng."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misolini ko'rib chiqaylik. Agar sizning hisoblangan oylik ish haqingiz 10 000 000 so'm bo'lsa: JShShS = 10 000 000 × 12% = 1 200 000 so'm; "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ish-haqi","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"IJPH"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" = 10 000 000 × 0,1% = 10 000 so'm; jami ushlanmalar = 1 210 000 so'm; qo'lingizga 8 790 000 so'm tushadi. Qo'shimcha ravishda ish beruvchi ijtimoiy soliq to'laydi: 10 000 000 × 12% = 1 200 000 so'm. IT Park xodimi uchun xuddi shu ish haqida: JShShS = 10 000 000 × 7,5% = 750 000 so'm, qo'lga — 9 240 000 so'm — farq oyiga 450 000 so'm."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Soliq kodeksida bir qator chegirmalar va ozod qilishlar nazarda tutilgan. JShShSga tortilmaydi: nafaqa, davlat pensiyalari, stipendiyalar, ish beruvchidan yiliga 4,22 "}],"$L